---
// How We Work - Timeline style
---

<section id="how-we-work" class="py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-6">
        How we work
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Scope fast. Ship fast. Scale continuously.
      </p>
    </div>
    <ol class="relative border-l-2 border-accent-500 ml-4">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <li class="mb-16 ml-6">
        <div class="absolute w-4 h-4 bg-accent-500 rounded-full -left-2 border-4 border-white"></div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Strategy Sprint</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2">Define what matters most, validate with data, and cut scope down to the highest-impact work.</p>
      </li>
      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <li class="mb-16 ml-6">
        <div class="absolute w-4 h-4 bg-accent-500 rounded-full -left-2 border-4 border-white"></div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Rapid Prototyping</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2">Build functional MVPs in weeks, not quarters.</p>
      </li>
      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <li class="ml-6">
        <div class="absolute w-4 h-4 bg-accent-500 rounded-full -left-2 border-4 border-white"></div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">System Extension</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2">Iterate and scale tools that integrate into your workflows and evolve with your team.</p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section> 